      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust A80 chassis powered by the venerable 2JZ-GTE inline-six. This unit retains its factory sequential twin-turbocharger configuration, delivering linear power through the sought-after Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. The drivetrain is anchored by a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Recent maintenance includes a full timing belt service and a comprehensive compression test confirming healthy PSI across all six cylinders. While the exterior displays minor patina consistent with a well-maintained driver-quality vehicle, the structural integrity and powertrain remain unmolested. Features original suspension geometry and factory-spec cooling systems, making this a prime candidate for the purist enthusiast.",
